        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1533806159" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9441658641865671572">The characterization of James Dean in this novel uses death as a primary tool. He is narrating from the grave. Though at peace, he prefers life, to the exact moment of the love he once knew. Interesting. Worth my time at night, at a toll booth. </span>

          </span>
