<span id="freeTextContainer11908839688355869228">Received this book through Goodreads Giveaways. I know little of James Dean and was looking forward to this read. I felt the passion of Dean, but not the relationship. At times was confused by Dean&apos;s thoughts. They jumped around too much. Realize Mr. Guevara was trying to channel his character. The book just didn&apos;t do much for me. </span>
